if you wouldn't tell Jim.

96
00:07:07,208 --> 00:07:09,301
Right.

97
00:07:09,408 --> 00:07:11,502
Are you ok?

98
00:07:11,607 --> 00:07:17,303
I'm fine. You're the one who looks
like she just saw a ghost.

99
00:07:20,808 --> 00:07:23,500
Why is it harder when
you're trying to get lost?

100
00:07:23,608 --> 00:07:26,600
You're doing great.
I have no idea where we are.

101
00:07:26,708 --> 00:07:29,303
Didn't we used to have a map in here?

102
00:07:29,408 --> 00:07:31,703
Hey, thanks for doing this.

103
00:07:31,805 --> 00:07:34,603
Do you think I'd let you come back out
on this road again by yourself?

104
00:07:34,707 --> 00:07:37,101
Aha! Map.

