120
00:09:01,705 --> 00:09:04,303
All right.

121
00:09:07,207 --> 00:09:09,500
What?

122
00:09:10,406 --> 00:09:12,602
- Looking for the midnight circle?
- What?

123
00:09:12,708 --> 00:09:16,100
Someone's going to die.

124
00:09:21,108 --> 00:09:23,003
See, now I know
we're going the wrong way.

125
00:09:23,105 --> 00:09:25,001
We're all the way
on the other side of town.

126
00:09:25,105 --> 00:09:27,500
Well, if I can just get the adrenaline
that's still coursing through my veins

