Hey, look, we can stop 
and ask for directions.

130
00:09:36,408 --> 00:09:38,102
I don't need directions.
I got it figured out.

131
00:09:38,206 --> 00:09:42,102
- I just need to find this one road.
- Wait a minute.

132
00:09:42,207 --> 00:09:47,400
