135
00:09:59,305 --> 00:10:01,803
Oh, no. I don't think there's
anything wrong with the car.

136
00:10:01,906 --> 00:10:04,002
Wow. That's cool.

137
00:10:04,105 --> 00:10:05,103
Do you mind?

138
00:10:05,205 --> 00:10:08,203
It's got the roll bar and the magnesium
wheels, 4-inch exhaust, right?

139
00:10:08,307 --> 00:10:09,803
Your  husband knows cars. Cool.

140
00:10:09,907 --> 00:10:12,801
While he's distracted, will you please
tell me how to get back to route 47?

141
00:10:12,906 --> 00:10:16,100
- Oh, yeah, let me write it down here.
- Thank you.

142
00:10:16,308 --> 00:10:19,700
- So, how long have you worked here?
- I own it.

143
00:10:19,807 --> 00:10:21,100
