144
00:10:21,203 --> 00:10:23,609
- I mean, not that that's...
- No, it's ok.

145
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:27,100
My father, he loved cars and he didn't
have a son fast forward, here I am,

146
00:10:27,204 --> 00:10:30,708
