150
00:10:39,608 --> 00:10:42,703
The road that you found me on last night...

151
00:10:42,806 --> 00:10:45,000
Do you know if there have been
any accidents there?

152
00:10:45,107 --> 00:10:47,500
You know, like serious
people dying accidents?

153
00:10:47,607 --> 00:10:50,500
- Not that I know of.
- Any other weird things?

154
00:10:50,608 --> 00:10:51,900
Weird like how?

155
00:10:52,008 --> 00:10:54,802
I don't know, weird like
cars going haywire,

156
00:10:54,905 --> 00:10:57,901
