- Thank you so much.

160
00:11:06,506 --> 00:11:10,500
- Have you ever heard of the
midnight circle? - What's that?

161
00:11:10,608 --> 00:11:14,201
- I don't know.
- Me neither.

162
00:11:14,307 --> 00:11:17,400
Ok, Joe. It's ready.

163
00:11:17,505 --> 00:11:20,602
