- Yeah, there was no listing.

170
00:11:39,805 --> 00:11:44,100
Huh. Thank you.
I'll see you next time.

171
00:11:46,907 --> 00:11:49,603
- Hey, mom.
- Hey, hey! How was school?

172
00:11:49,707 --> 00:11:51,800
- I need $10.
