218
00:15:11,006 --> 00:15:12,800
Are you?

219
00:15:12,907 --> 00:15:15,502
Well, yes.

220
00:15:15,905 --> 00:15:20,001
Get on there. Get on there.
I'm telling you to get on there.

221
00:15:20,106 --> 00:15:22,102
