thing planned out.

232
00:15:49,108 --> 00:15:51,302
- I was warned you were in a bad mood.
- Yeah, I'm in a bad mood

233
00:15:51,405 --> 00:15:54,401
because some people really know
how to get under my skin, ok?

234
00:15:54,505 --> 00:15:56,400
Now, where's my hammer?
I don't even have my hammer now.

235
00:15:56,507 --> 00:15:59,403
I had my hammer right here.
I'm losing my mind.

236
00:15:59,508 --> 00:16:01,301
Looking for this?

237
00:16:01,406 --> 00:16:04,003
Yes, I am. And you know what?
I've had just about as much aggravation

238
00:16:04,108 --> 00:16:05,700
as I can stand for one day, thank you.

239
00:16:05,806 --> 00:16:07,902
Ok, sorry. Bad timing.

240
00:16:08,007 --> 00:16:10,601
